<td style="width:30%;" rowspan="1">Preceded<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>by<br/><span style="font-weight: bold"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ur-Zababa" title="Ur-Zababa">Ur-Zababa</a></span></td>
